  2,197,"ňĻCommitment toňļ pilgrimage is made in appointed months.¬†Whoever commits to ňĻperformingňļ pilgrimage, let them stay away from intimate relations, foul language, and arguments during pilgrimage. Whatever good you do, Allah ňĻfullyňļ knows of it. Take ňĻnecessaryňļ provisions ňĻfor the journeyňļ‚ÄĒsurely the best provision is righteousness. And be mindful of Me, O people of reason"
